snippet.title: "I Have A Baby Now" Amber Heard Explains Why She Will "Never Go To Prison"
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Just Stated That She Can't Go To Prison Because Of Her Newly Born Baby!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

It seems like Amber Heard has just turned into the mother of a baby daughter and she seems confident that she won’t be going to prison thanks to her as she confidently said: “I can’t go behind bars now with a child”. 

But many think that this is no problem and that she will end up in jail anyway. Back in July first, Heard posted a picture of herself holding a baby on Instagram which surprised everyone because she had never mentioned anything even remotely referring to a pregnancy. Another fact many fans pointed out was that the baby looked at least a few months old but that isn’t very surprising after you find out it was a surrogate baby because she has several medical issues that prevent her from having a child. However, is the baby really a good enough reason to dodge prison?

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
